OL,3,CMan jailed after shaken baby suffers
OL,4,Csignificant injuries
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for more than
OL,7,Fthree years for shaking a baby,
OL,8,Fleaving the child with significant
OL,9,Finjuries.
OL,11,FThe baby was treated at the Royal
OL,12,FBlackburn Hospital for multiple bleeds
OL,13,Fon the brain on 20 February, 2024.
OL,14,FAfter an investigation, Dylan Saville,
OL,15,F26, was arrested on suspicion of
OL,16,Fassault causing Grievous Bodily Harm.
OL,18,FAt the time of his arrest, he denied
OL,19,Fthe offence and faked concern for the
OL,20,Fbaby.
