OL,3,CMan jailed after shaken baby suffers
OL,4,Csignificant injuries
OL,6,FIt was found that he assaulted the
OL,7,Fchild by shaking, leaving the baby boy
OL,8,Fwith significant injuries.
OL,10,FSaville, from West Yorkshire, pleaded
OL,11,Fguilty at Burnley Crown Court, and has
OL,12,Fbeen sentenced to three years and six
OL,13,Fmonths in prison.
OL,15,FDC Shanaz Kone, from the East Child
OL,16,FProtection Team, said: "Saville
OL,17,Fassaulted a baby - one of the most
OL,18,Finnocent members of our society, who
OL,19,Fwill be left with lifelong effects
OL,20,Ffrom his injuries.
