OL,6,F"My thoughts are with the baby, and
OL,7,Fhis loved ones as he continues to
OL,8,Frecover. The severity of his injuries
OL,9,Fshows how this could have easily had a
OL,10,Fdifferent, heartbreaking outcome.
OL,12,F"It has been a real team effort within
OL,13,FChild Protection to secure a
OL,14,Fconviction and it is not for me to
OL,15,Fcomment on the sentence, but I do hope
OL,16,Fthe knowledge that Saville had been
OL,17,Fbrought to justice and will spend time
OL,18,Fbehind bars brings some comfort to the
OL,19,Fbaby's family."
